headline: NOT A POLITICAL PARTY
sentences: The Post's report states the agreement has made it possible for the national party to fund the campaign of Cheney challenger Harriet Hageman, who the party has now recognized as the presumptive nominee for Cheney's seat.

According to The Washington Post, leaders of the Wyoming GOP have privately signed an unprecedented agreement that opens the door to them funding a challenger to Rep. Liz Cheney (R-WY) in a primary this year.
They officially have become the party of do as we say? not what is honest, correct or patriotic.
The QOP has officially become either a crime syndicate or a terrorist organization.
Nothing more needs to be said.
